social_posts.post_text: Introducing Mike Alvarez, the newest artist to join the Love Soul family in the new year. He Is a talented singer songwriter with a fresh upbeat sound that is guaranteed to put a smile on your face. Stay tuned for his debut single "She Got Me" dropping next Friday January 13th on all digital platforms 🎙️🕶️
“She Got Me” debut single by @mikealvarez__ will be out on all digital platforms this Friday the 13th!

“She Got Me” the debut single by Mike Alvarez out on all digital platforms! an upbeat love ballad  reminiscent of gospel. Uplifting with smooth vocals, amazing sax solos and beautiful harmonies. The perfect song to dedicate to that special someone. 🎙️🎷

Vocals - Mike Alvarez @mikealvarez__ 
Bg Vocals - Fernanda Valdivia @valdiviafn 
Bg Vocals - Kendall Coyer @kendallcoyer 
Drums - Alex Blanco @alexivanblancojr 
Guitar, Bass - Johnny Rico @theejohnnyrico 
Saxophone - Brandon Muhawi @bmuhawi 
Organ, Recorded, Mixed and Mastered - Adam Valenzuela 
@adamvalenzuelamusic
